// Rafa's brain — a curated knowledge base with a lightweight intent matcher.
//
// Each entry carries many trigger keywords/synonyms, so a single entry answers
// a wide spread of phrasings (the ~90 entries below cover far more than 90
// literal questions). matchRafa() scores entries by how many of their triggers
// appear in the normalized query and returns the best hit, or null so the UI
// can offer suggestions. Everything here mirrors what the app actually does —
// if a mechanic changes, update the matching entry so Rafa never lies.

import { SIMPLE_MODE } from '../config';

